description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'How To Start Weighted Calisthenics | THENX' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow the same steps I took to learning how to start weighted calisthenics!
